title: Tommy Sandoval: Ricta Slix
description:
Chula's finest and Street League Vet Tommy Sandoval hits Lakeside Skatepark with the Ricta Slix! The Slix combine our NRG Formula, with a custom molded TPU slide insert for three times more slip and minimal drag on the inside of the wheel for longer and faster grinds. 81b, so they're hard AND fast!

SAC STORYTELLERS
"DUB MILITIA"
